<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<title>Document Release Notification</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color:#f4f6f9; padding:20px;">

<table width="750" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
       style="background-color:#ffffff; padding:25px; border-radius:8px;">

    <tr>
        <td style="font-size:18px; font-weight:bold; color:#003366;">
            #CompanyName#
        </td>
    </tr>

    <tr><td height="20"></td></tr>

    <tr>
        <td>Dear Team,</td>
    </tr>

    <tr><td height="10"></td></tr>

    <tr>
        <td>
            The following document has been released on the AQMS Portal is now available for use.
        </td>
    </tr>

    <tr><td height="20"></td></tr>

    <tr>
        <td>
            <table border="1" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse:collapse;">
                <tr style="background:#e9ecef; font-weight:bold;">
                    <td>CPR No.</td>
                    <td>Released Date</td>
                    <td>Process/Department</td>
                    <td>Doc. No.</td>
                    <td>Doc. Name</td>
                    <td>Doc Rev. No.</td>
                    
                    <td>Doc. Category</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>#CPRNumber#</td>
                    <td>#ReleaseDate#</td>
                    <td>#Department#</td>
                    <td>#DocNumber#</td>
                    <td>#DocName#</td>
                    <td>#RevisionNo#</td>
                    
                    <td>#DocCategory#</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>

    <tr><td height="25"></td></tr>

    <tr>
        <td>
            You may access the document by navigating to: 
            <b>Login → Dashboard → Level → Document Category</b> (as mentioned in the table above)
        </td>
    </tr>

    <tr><td height="15"></td></tr>

    <tr>
        <td>
            Portal Link : <a href="#PortalLink#">#PortalLink#</a>
        </td>
    </tr>

    <tr><td height="30"></td></tr>

    <tr style="display:none">
        <td style="font-size:12px; color:#777;">
            This is an automated email from AQMS System.
        </td>
    </tr>

</table>

</body>
</html>
